Description: Political intrigue abounds! What happened between Danzo, the leader of Konoha, and his brother, Itachi? And where does Naruto fit in?
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 51
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 12
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Two brothers harmed in a ritual that was half magic/half science seek the legendary Philosopher’s Stone to make things right.
Title: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST, VOL. 25
Author: Hiromu Arakawa

Description: In this romantic comedy, Haruhi, a poor girl at a rich school, is forced to work — as a boy — for the school’s all-male club.
Title: OURAN HIGH SCHOOL HOST CLUB, VOL. 16
Author: Bisco Hatori

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 2
Author: Kato Kazue

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 35
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry. Do they have what it takes?
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 5
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Isn't being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy. In this volume: has the temporary safe haven dulled their edge? No worries, there are secrets even here.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 4
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Monkey D. Luffy, who has the power to stretch like rubber, searches with a motley crew of would-be pirates for a legendary treasure called "One Piece."
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 57
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 1
Author: Kazue Kato
